Randy J. Goodwin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Randy_J._Goodwin 0 Randy J. Goodwin, born as Ivan Jerome Goodwin, is a Hollywood actor. He is perhaps best known for his role as "Kennedy Winslow" on Fast Track and "Max Ellis" on the show Abby, as well as his recurring roles on Girlfriends as "Davis Hamilton" and The Vampire Diaries as "Dr. Jonas Martin".
